üîÑ SSR Flow

  • 1. Browser requests page
  • 2. Server queries database
  • 3. Server renders HTML
  • 4. Server sends complete page
  • 5. Browser displays immediately
Result: Fresh data, slower response

‚ö° SSG Flow

  • 1. Browser requests page
  • 2. CDN checks cache
  • 3. CDN serves pre-built HTML
  • 4. Browser displays immediately
  • 5. Server never touched!
Result: Lightning fast, minimal cost

üíª CSR Flow

  • 1. Browser requests page
  • 2. Server sends empty HTML
  • 3. Browser loads JavaScript
  • 4. Browser makes API call
  • 5. Server processes & responds
  • 6. Browser renders with data
Result: Interactive, visible loading

üéØ Manager Demo Script

1. Visual Impact: "Watch these logs - you can see exactly what happens behind the scenes for each method."

2. SSR Demo: "Notice how SSR hits the database twice, processes on server, then sends complete HTML. Fresh data, but expensive."

3. SSG Demo: "Look at SSG - only 5 steps, served from CDN, server never touched. This is why it's 90% cheaper."

4. CSR Demo: "CSR takes the most steps - empty page first, then JavaScript loads and makes API calls. Good for interactivity, bad for SEO."

5. Cost Impact: "The table shows real costs - SSG is 10x cheaper than SSR per request."
